cs.CL, cs.SI, cs.SD, cs.CY, cs.LG

This paper belongs to the field of computational linguistics (cs.CL) as it deals with the analysis of language in social media platforms. The paper also involves machine learning techniques for classification, which falls under the sub-category of social and information retrieval (cs.SI) and statistical learning (cs.LG). The analysis of frequency and classification of irony markers also involves data mining and analysis (cs.SD) and natural language processing (cs.CY).
